Creating a post 

1 as a user, when I click on submit a request, I am asked for my email address (done)
2 as as user when I request a post, a request is saved in the db with unique code per request (done)
3 an email is sent to the users with unique code to submit their post link ie www.15minutesoffame.com/SDF87SF8SD8F9 (ui and backend done but not email sending)
4 check if the unique is expired,  create a expired link page (done)


cache
